title: Added English Language support on the UI when the phone when the phone language is set to English.
message:
Added English Language support on the UI when the phone when the phone language is set to English.

Still not tested on actual phone.

title: Separated system logic from tracked object logic to
message:
Separated system logic from tracked object logic to
make it easier to modify the app to collect data
on different objects in the future.

At this point the changes are not well tested. They
need to be tested on hardware - especially the GPS
and email functions.
